title: 047 collection (047, nollfyrasju, salkin, soda, pricky, bitpop )
description:
Since some people at last.fm were requesting it, I'm uploading some fine bitpop music by the band 047 which disbanded in 2007 (I guess). Too bad, because they were awesome.
This is what I've got, it's not complete but at least it's something.
If someone has the Arvika gig recorded, please let me know.
